00:28:26.650 --> 00:28:28.970
but authorship dispute.

00:28:28.970 --> 00:28:34.190
They say that the ORI, the
Office of Research Integrity,

00:28:34.190 --> 00:28:38.980
considers many disputes
between the collaborators

00:28:38.980 --> 00:28:42.810
on the same research project
as an authorship dispute

00:28:42.810 --> 00:28:46.120
or credit disputes
rather than plagiarism.

00:28:46.120 --> 00:28:47.920
So, I would ask your insights.

00:28:47.920 --> 00:28:54.340
How could make the interaction
between policy and the law?

00:28:54.340 --> 00:28:55.270
